To Integrate Git with Jenkins, Try the following

ManageJenkins-> manage plugins-> "search for Git plugin" (install)

To configure Git to a jenkins job

Click on 
Job->Configure->(under sourcecode management select GIT)->Git ---Give repository URL

Select
Build Trigger-> pool SCM
and give th schedule as * * * * *
## so whenever a git hub get commited then the jenkins run the job in local shell or bash command.
